 simmering basket instead of measuring cup onto mixing bowl lid."},{"content":"Add water, tomatoes, courgettes, celery, carrot, chickpeas, kidney beans, cannellini beans, stock paste, chilli flakes and reserved chopped herbs then cook <b>20 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Transfer into a thermal serving bowl or other large bowl and stir through reserved Parmesan. Garnish with extra shaved Parmesan to taste and serve with crusty bread."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <em>The Basic Cookbook <\/em>for a vegetable stock paste recipe.","<strong>Vegetarian Tuscan Bean Soup:<\/strong> Omit the pancetta and reduce sautéing time to 3 minutes in step 4. Proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","50m","6 portions"]}